Usage
-----

Copy /usr/share/doc/rubygems-mirror/mirrorrc.example to $(HOME)/.gems/.mirrorrc,
Edit .mirrorrc, change 'to:' paramerter ::

  ---
  - from: http://rubygems.org
    to:   /var/lib/mirror/gems
    parallelism: 10


Execute next command for mirroring.::

  $ rake -f /usr/share/doc/rubygems-mirror/Rakefile mirror:update

